title: Will vNutz ever return?
body: One day our little twelvie will come back to us or so the prophecies foretell.

replies.body: I think he moved on and got a life.
We all know he secretly watches us all in the deep of night drinking Ravs special Red Drink and Dowitos.

He could be any of us, using a false name, luring us all into suspecting each other to be vNutz so that we organise witch hunts and turn on each other.
The real twist is that we are ALL vNutz.
